(3855, 256, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_1', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">#wardrobe #clothes #dressingroom #furniture #style #cosiness #interior #design #architecture #spacefilling #space-filling</span></p>\r\n<p>If you are not sure whether to have a whole room as your wardrobe, « open » wardrobes are exactly what you need. Separated by glass panels, such wardrobes will become part of your room, but at the same time they will perform their function. The advantage of such an organisation is that all clothes are always before your eyes, and the wardrobe gets enough natural light. You have a fantastic sense of fashion or an impressive shoe collection ? Why not make it the jewel of your room ?!</p>'),
