(3865, 256, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_2', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">#wardrobe #clothes #dressingroom #furniture #style #cosiness #interior #design #architecture #LemaMobili #spacefilling </span></p>\r\n<p>If you however do not have enough space for such an ambitious wardrobe, do not become discouraged. Even an ordinary closet can be handy and practical, just find a good place for it in your room. For the closet not to look cumbersome, it is better to build it into the walls, to equip it with doors from floor to ceiling, and to choose a neutral finishing. It may serve not only to keep clothes, but also as a separation wall dividing the space into zones.</p>'),
