(4228, 253, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_0', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">#interior #design #space #comfort #bedroom #livingroom #texture #colors #shape #geometry #embroidery #furniture #paints #pillows #decoration #sofa #chairs #carpets #architexture #ornaments #accent #atmosphere #originality #blue #darkblue#indigo #brightcolors #brostecopenhagen</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Indigo is great as a neutral background: deep blue walls and ceilings make all the colorful design elements and accessories look just amazing. The perception of dark blue depends on its associate colors. In order to counteract a depressing shade or to create a bright punch in your interior, use furniture made of light or red wood, and also contrast colors, such as pink, orange, yellow and red.</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #993300;"><a style="color: #993300;" href="http://hskjalp.dk" target="_blank">hskjalp.dk</a></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #993300;"><strong><a style="color: #993300;" href="http://brostecopenhagen.com/" target="_blank">brostecopenhagen.com</a></strong></span></p>'),
