(4237, 253, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_1', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">#interior #design #space #comfort #bedroom #livingroom #texture #colors #shape #geometry #embroidery #furniture #paints #pillows #decoration #sofa #chairs #carpets #architexture #ornaments #accent #atmosphere #originality #blue #darkblue#indigo #brightcolors #brostecopenhagen#hskjalmp #orange #wood #mint</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>White elements are a must in a dark blue interior. The classic and all-time favorite combination of blue and white always looks stylish and intriguing. Just like porcelain, lace, and various ornaments and patterns, blue and white design in the interior is a sign of aristocracy and traditions.</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #993300;"><strong><a style="color: #993300;" href="http://brostecopenhagen.com/" target="_blank">brostecopenhagen.com</a></strong></span></p>'),
