(4246, 253, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_2', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">#interior #design #space #comfort #bedroom #livingroom #texture #colors #shape #geometry #furniture #decoration #sofa #chairs #carpets #orange #wood#architexture #ornaments #accent #atmosphere #originality #blue #darkblue#indigo #brightcolors #brostecopenhagen</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want to beautify your interior with indigo color, go for smaller rooms. Dark blue will visually remove the borders, and the room will look spacial and cozy. Such a trick will do for cabinets, small bedrooms, and libraries,  as the color is easy on the eye for any occasion. Dark blue interiors with golden and silver details look especially elegant.</p>'),
