(4256, 253, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_3', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">#interior #design #space #comfort #bedroom #livingroom #texture #colors #shape #geometry #embroidery #furniture #paints #pillows #decoration #sofa #chairs #carpets #architexture #ornaments #accent #atmosphere #originality #blue #darkblue#indigo #brightcolors #orange #wood</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Indigo color is one of the best options to use at the kitchens, because shades of blue suppress appetite, and contributes to deep concentration and spatial perception. Choosing design of a kitchen, dark blue should be used as an additional color punch, bright and saturated. For instance, rugs, candles, or table-ware can be indigo. Any abundant color is irritating, and thus can call for negative emotions, that’s why choosing color boosts wisely is rather important.</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #993300;"><a style="color: #993300;" href="http://hskjalp.dk/" target="_blank">hskjalp.dk</a></span></strong></p>'),
