(4474, 637, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_1', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">#</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">modern classic #classic #white #yellow #livingroom #furniture #style #elegance #interior #design</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">#architecture</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">#</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Busnelli #Miniforms </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">#spacefilling</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Furniture is the element, which allows perceiving the space correctly. It is advisable to choose furniture in which soft smooth curves and rigid lines ideally complement each other, without arguing with the atmosphere of the room. Using different textures – light and solid, shiny and matted, you may introduce accents and achieve an effect of harmony.</span></p>'),
