(4988, 701, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_sources_2_link-_crb_image_link_2', 'www.bloglovin.com'),
(4989, 701, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_sources_2_link-_crb_image_link_3', 'resonances2.tumblr.com'),
(4990, 701, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_2', '<p style="text-align: center;">#modern classic #classic #beige #livingroom #furniture #style #elegance #interior #design #architecture # Busnelli # Miniforms #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p>Lighting is probably one of the most important aspects of any interior as it is capable to emphasize all merits of the space. Windows, framed with curtains, are of course the source of natural daylight. The curtains themselves may stand out, however, most often they complete the image of the space and are of neutral colours.</p>\r\n<p>You are not obliged to use a traditional crystal ceiling lamp as the main lighting element in the room. Several sources of light will diversify the space. Lighting, like furniture, plays a practical role, providing light where needed. Honesty is the slogan of the modern style. The lighting should be honest; it should serve to light the rest zones, to ease reading, to have a meal, to highlight paintings, etc. The modern lighting items may add some stylish spice to your interior.</p>'),
