(4996, 701, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_3', '<p>#modern classic #classic #light #grey #furniture #style #unusual #interior #design #architecture # B&amp;BItalia # Brokis #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p>Accessories will give a special charm to the classical style. As accessories, use both modern fancy decor with various textures and classical elements - sculptures, paintings, vases. Large abstract paintings, or small paired originally-shaped tables will look innovative in the classical interior. You may put accents on the sofa and armchairs by ways of bright pillows or blankets. Harmoniously placed, they will integrate themselves in the design of your space.</p>'),
