(5024, 708, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_0', '<p style="text-align: center;">#workspace #office # workroom #workplace #furniture #style #coffee #girl #interior #design #architecture #Busnelli #LemaMobili #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p>“Green office”</p>\r\n<p>“Green office” or ecological office is a modern office space where everything helps increasing not only the productivity, but also the care for health of the working person. Pay special attention to the correct lighting of the working place. The natural light should fall on the table from the left side, whereas the artificial one should light the whole space in a bright and homogeneous way. If possible, the working place should be close to the window, - no matter the view, it will allow the eyes to rest or, on the contrary, to focus on an idea. Furthermore, it will make the person feel closer to his/her natural habitat.</p>'),
