(5042, 708, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_sources_3_link-_crb_image_link_1', 'www.mmlampadari.com'),
(5043, 708, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_sources_3_link-_crb_image_link_2', 'abbycox.tumblr.com'),
(5044, 708, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_3', '<p style="text-align: center;">#workspace #office # workroom #workplace #furniture #style #blue #plant #light #interior #design #architecture # HSkjalmp #LemaMobili #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In the working bustle of office life, it is important not to forget the rest zone. A neatly organised corner with a soft armchair under a soft lamp light will help to relax and forget the work concerns. If there is no way to have a separate zone, grasp to the decoration elements such as vivid plants or flowers which remind of nature and rest, or sculpture figures which will make you think of something other than your work, for instance, of your past and future travels!</p>'),
