(5074, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_0', '<p style="text-align: center;">#metal #silver # livingroom #furniture #style # shine #girl #fashion #interior #design #architecture # Arketipo #Brokis #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Despite the traditional purely utilitarian use of metal in construction and production, today metal wares are often used in interior decoration. Metal is one of the natural and most ancient materials used by human beings, which is why it combines harmoniously with other natural textures – wood, stone, ceramics, glass, and plaster. Large wall panels from matted unpolished metal will suit for bars, lofts, men’s salons and bachelor interiors where the brutality of metal comes in handy to emphasize the rough male spirit. The other decoration variant is a metal mosaic. Apart from resistance to any impact, a metal mosaic is also a shiny sparkling panel picture, scale and sea ripple, sun flecks or shine of treasures – it will certainly become a bright accent of any interior.</p>'),
(5075, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subtitle_1', ''),
(5076, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_1_image-_crb_d_image_0', '717'),
(5077, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_sources_1_link-_crb_image_link_0', 'shareenjoel.com'),
(5078, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_sources_1_link-_crb_image_link_1', 'thepropdispensary.com'),
(5079, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_1', '<p style="text-align: center;">#metal #silver #grey # livingroom #furniture #style # wood #girl #fashion #interior #design #architecture #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The modern design strives for honesty, telling us how objects are actually made. Their inside frame has gradually become visible and a trend of the last years. A metallic frame is transparent, graceful; it emphasizes the structure and reveals details. It is everywhere – from storage racks, bearing parts of furniture, table and chair legs, to lamps and decoration. The frame geometry is ideal – it inspires painters, graphic artists, tile, wallpaper and tissue producers. The line structures create an atmosphere of lightness, weightlessness, transparency, and easily fit in any interior.</p>'),
(5080, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subtitle_2', ''),
(5081, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_2_image-_crb_d_image_0', '718'),
(5082, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_sources_2_link-_crb_image_link_0', 'leibal.com'),
