(5085, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_2', '<p style="text-align: center;">#metal #silver #grey #texture #kitchen #furniture #style #wood #girl #fashion #interior #design #architecture #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Do not hesitate to use metal everywhere. Modern designers actively use different types of metal and their imitations for finishings of furniture facades and working surfaces, in particular in the kitchen. Aside from traditional stainless steel, precious metals are greatly in vogue – bronze, gilding, copper. Golden surfaces, shiny details and accessories create an atmosphere of luxury, chic, and refer to the design of the 70’s, challenge and bring in some festive mood in your everyday life.</p>'),
