(5095, 715, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_4', '<p>Metallic accessories are a real catch for owners of small apartments. Polished surfaces reflect the light and visually enlarge the space, while an interesting decoration imitating precious metals may add some glamour to your interior. Do not forget the details: vases, candleholders, mirrors made of expensive types of metal; they will complete the look of your interior and add a luxury note to the image.</p>'),
