(5124, 723, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_0', '<p style="text-align: center;">#kitchen #brown #beige #furniture #style #children #food #coffee #interior #design #architecture # Pedini #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you correctly choose the colour of your kitchen space, even a usual morning coffee and a simple oat porridge will be much more pleasant. Even if you are not an expert in colouristic, it is easy to understand the influence of colours on appetite. It is no secret that orange and turquoise shades and their combinations stimulate the appetite. However, do not give unlimited green light to the bright colours, be very careful to use them in the kitchen. It is best to use soft shades of these colours instead of their saturated bright variants. Whereas thanks to dark and warm shades, the kitchen will seem more homey and cosy. Nonetheless, when choosing the colour, listen to your feelings and emotions.</p>'),
