(5138, 723, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_2', '<p style="text-align: center;">#kitchen #colour #marble #metal #furniture #style #children #interior #design #architecture #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">From the earliest times all lords, kings, knights, peasants gathered together around a big table to share food. The times have changed, but the role of the dinner zone remains the same – it unites, invites to sincere talks, and decorates the eating process. The dinner zone is the major accent of a kitchen or a dining room. The table and chairs should be comfortable, but in order to diversify the interior, you may choose chairs of different colours and textures, however, of no more than three different shades. Make sure that the table is well lit to see the food and the people sitting around it. A large singular lamp or a group of several hanging lamps will offer the best solution, as they maintain the general style of the kitchen and become a bright self-sufficient element of the interior.</p>'),
(5139, 723, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subtitle_3', ''),
(5140, 723, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_3_image-_crb_d_image_0', '728'),
