(5311, 731, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_3', '<p style="text-align: center;">#colour #mustard #yellow #blue #emerald #livingroom #furniture #style # autumn #cosiness #interior #design #architecture #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you however do not want to overdose this unconventional complicated colour, you may just limit yourself to the mustard-coloured furniture. It will still be interesting and stylish, but less drastic. Such furniture will harmoniously fit in the room where light pastel colours reign. In this case, you will obtain a balanced picture – the calming wall colour will downplay the excessive brightness of the mustard colour.</p>'),
