(5318, 731, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_4', '<p style="text-align: center;">#colour #mustard #yellow #white #beige #livingroom #furniture #style # autumn #cosiness #interior #design #architecture # Miniforms #Muuto #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Mustard-coloured accessories and textile will flesh out well the atmosphere of your interior. Light accents in the form of curtains ; a nice rug to walk upon barefoot like upon autumnal leaves ; a cosy throw blanket on the sofa ; pillows with interesting patterns ; or unconventional glass vases will bring into your home a taste of a romantic autumn, without overloading the space. Such elements are easy to replace depending on your mood!</p>'),
