(5335, 750, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_0', '<p style="text-align: center;">#lightning #livingroom #furniture #style #girl #cosiness #interior #design #architecture #bocci #Zanotta #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">A clear tendency of modern design is the use of geometry in every way possible. It is also noticeable in elements of lighting. Such conciseness, lightness and openness of form make way for the actual purpose: the light itself. Simple geometry shows the modernity and functionality of the lamp, whereas the material refers to certain conditions of use. A pendant light made of black metal is associated with industrial lighting in the loft style. A lampshade of polished brass reminds us of echoes of the cosy Provence. Gold adds splendour and elegance.</p>'),
(5336, 750, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subtitle_1', ''),
(5337, 750, '_designs_block_block-_crb_row_images_1_image-_crb_d_image_0', '747'),
