(5349, 750, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_2', '<p style="text-align: center;">#lightning #concrete #livingroom #furniture #style #girl #interior #design #architecture #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In case your interior needs more style and transparency, the solution for you are glass pendant lights ! Modern glass forms can be simple, for example round, or more sophisticated. This is one of the most interesting options if you want to preserve as much light as possible. In addition, glass combined with a mirror will look even more beneficial for your interior.</p>'),
