(5355, 750, '_designs_block_block-_crb_subcontent_3', '<p style="text-align: center;">#lightning #glass #livingroom #furniture #style #girl #interior #design #architecture #TomDixon #spacefilling</p>\r\n<p>Lamps beyond time and space</p>\r\n<p>For a bold interior, some kind of futuristic accessory is necessary. For example, a daring metallic pendant light. This will emphasize your independence of time and standards. This kind of lamps can become the main accent of your home !</p>'),
