(108, 1, '2017-03-04 10:37:24', '2017-03-04 10:37:24', 'Please meet our young, creative and enthusiastic team! It is composed of amazing professionals who love what they do. We have a vivid imagination and a plenty of ideas how to realize the most audacious desires of our clients in interior design. We are ready to challenge ourselves and to find the solution that suits the client to perfection!<span class="moment-readmore">Read more</span>\r\n\r\nWe developed the innovative on-line approach to the interior design process. Taking into account your desires and requirements, Space-Filling develop a 3D project of your new home and recommend you the furniture you need. We will add value to your space, in such a way that you will feel happy and comfy at home.\r\n\r\nSpace-Filling offers interior design services entirely online, which means you can design your space from the comfort of your home, your office, or even on-the- go using your internet-accessible device. And no hourly fees here! With our service, you\'ll pay a one-time flat fee per room to receive complete design services from our talented Space-Filling designers.\r\n\r\nOur platform is an interior design online service provided by professional architects and interior designers of our 3D design agency located in Brussels, Belgium. Based on the measurements and plans of the space provided by a client, we will make a 3D design project for the space, whether it will be a shop design, an office design, a restaurant design, or any other interior design project. We will recommend you the furniture which will complete the look of your space. The project will be easy to realize. We will be happy to tell you everything about the latest interior design trends.', 'Our team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-team', '', '', '2017-05-16 19:23:00', '2017-05-16 17:23:00', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?page_id=108', 0, 'page', '', 0),
