(235, 1, '2017-03-27 18:29:10', '2017-03-27 16:29:10', 'Furniture with plump sides, cheesy armrests, surprising simplicity, outstanding color and geometrical concepts, radiograms and commodes - all remarkable signs of the 50’s style are coming back to our interiors.\r\nRetro is the spirit of the past. The 50’s of the last century became an amazing postwar era, making the young people stand for liberty and peace. The same trends could be seen in the interiors of that time. The world tried to forget all the horror and create a happy new reality. Retro style is something diverse, amusing, yet complicated which is meant to mix the unmixable.\r\nThe 50’s style is very popular and topical these days. The most colorful, outstanding and remarkable elements of the past century are a must while creating the modern interiors. Rooms and places are filled with functional and comfortable elements which don’t seem to be a good match from the first sight.\r\nThe 50’s style furniture can look quite unpredictable. Unusual shape is considered to be the main feature of the retro style. Bulbous and round shapes of the objects create quite a comfortable and peaceful atmosphere in the room. This explains why our current market is experiencing a great demand for the retro furniture.', 'RETRO STYLE', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'retro-style__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-23 13:47:55', '2017-06-23 11:47:55', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?p=235', 0, 'post', '', 0),
