(253, 1, '2017-03-28 20:30:23', '2017-03-28 18:30:23', '<p>Deep, saturated, impressive blue is used in modern interiors more and more often. The aquamarine shade can be examined infinitely, as it is brave and complicated on one hand, but on the other hand, it’s so universal. Just like beige color, dark blue can fit into any interior: from avant-garde to minimalism to classic English style. Depending on the lights, indigo changes in completely different ways, that’s why using the color in the interior is not always a simple task.</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #993300;"><strong><a style="color: #993300;" href="http://brostecopenhagen.com/" target="_blank">brostecopenhagen.com</a></strong></span></p>', 'Indigo', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'indigo__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-23 13:47:55', '2017-06-23 11:47:55', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?p=253', 0, 'post', '', 0),
