(256, 1, '2017-03-28 20:34:01', '2017-03-28 18:34:01', '<p>Our usual morning starts with a bathroom, a coffee, breakfast and, of course, an important decision – what to wear today. Clothing is part of our image and of our everyday life. Whether you have lots of clothes or just a sufficient amount, they should have a separate place in your home. The location and the size of the wardrobe depend on the possibilities of your home. It may be a simple standing clothes rail, or a wardrobe, or even a walk-in closet. It can become the realisation of your possibilities or ambitions, it helps organise the clothes and the space, but it is important to think through its configuration.</p>', 'Dressing', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'dressing__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-23 13:47:55', '2017-06-23 11:47:55', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?p=256', 0, 'post', '', 0),
