ners can help with projects big and small. Whether you’re making over a whole room or just want a second opinion on that new paint color, they’re ready to jump in with qualified advice and suggestions for your project.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Why choose Space-Filling over a traditional interior designer?\r\n1. Access to top designers all across the nation regardless of where you are.\r\n2. Enjoy the convenience of being able to design your space entirely online.\r\n3. Share your inspiration and feedback without the challenge of scheduling in-person meetings.\r\n4. Save money with our low-cost design fee and great prices on furniture and home decor.\r\n5. You set your own timeline of completion so you can work within your budget. You can have an affordable room makeover design now and not have to cough up a huge furniture budget all at once.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">When should I use Space-Filling?\r\nYou can use Space-Filling whenever you need interior design help. No matter what your design needs are, we have the service to fit them.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I am not sure I want a makeover, what else does your site offer?\r\nIf you’re uncertain if a makeover is right for you, we have plenty of other services for you to check out! We offer educational and inspiring blog content, a complementary design quiz, and curated product finds. Sign up for an account and our regular emails will keep you posted on upcoming celebrity designers, trending design tips, and sweepstake.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I live outside Europe, can Space-Filling design my space?\r\nYou can order a design project from any place of the world but only a rendered design and a recommended furniture list. At this time Space-Filling can offer a full completed design project with furniture list and shopping opportunities only within the Europe.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Do I have to take the Style Quiz?\r\nNo, it’s not required but it’s helpful for us to match your needs. Don’t over think the quiz, it’s meant to be fun. It’s complimentary and “scary accurate”.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Design process\r\nWhat do I need to start a project?\r\nTo start a project you need to have a plan of your space with all measurements and some photos of this space which you will upload to the database as well as filling out a questionnaire. If you have them all ready to go just click Get Started!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">What will I get at the end of a project?\r\nIn 2 weeks after the receiving your questionnaire and room measurements, you will get a fully designed proposal which includes a high-quality 3d visualization of your space, drawing with all the furniture and their sizes, the furniture items list with pricing and a 3d panoramic view to see your design ideas come to life.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">What is 3d panoramic view?\r\nA 3d panoramic view is a 360-degree image of your interior. To watch it you can use our application or special link on our web-site. For best results, open it on your device standing in the center of your space and turn your body.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">What is involved in the design process?\r\n1) Click Get Started and complete the questionnaire to help us understand your vision\r\n2) Within 24 hours you will receive by e-mail your questionnaire results and the pricing of your project.\r\n3) We take a deposit of 50% of the quoted price before starting work\r\n4) Within 5 working days you will receive your initial design concept. You are free to make any changes in this step.\r\n5) The remaining payment is required and once payment is received the designer will finalize the project and within 5 days you will receive the completed interior design project.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">What exactly is the initial concept?\r\nThe initial concept is a midpoint design that is 60% completed. It shows you the major furnishings, color scheme, and general direction the interior designer has in mind for your space. Your feedback is essential for our designer to get to the final design. Immediately after receiving your input, your designer will get back to work to complete your final design plan.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">What if I need to make a second change in the design project?\r\nNot a problem! After receiving the first design concept you are welcome to make one change to the design concept and in a few days you will receive the full complete interior project. If you wish to make another change to the finalized plans, you can send us a request and our designers will make the change for an additional fee of half the price initially quoted.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">When will I receive my initial design concept?\r\nWithin 24 hours you will receive the results of your questionnaire as well as the pricing for the project. With your approval and payment, your designer will begin working on your project. You will receive one initial concept design delivered to your inbox within 5 working days. Have a rush design project? Let us know and we will do our best to accommodate your timeline.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Managing Your Account\r\nWhere do I manage my account?\r\nIn the upper right-hand side, next to the search icon you will find your profile. From there you can manage:\r\n∙ Your Projects - access to existing and previous Room Designs\r\n∙ Settings - update your contact information and email preferences\r\nWhat if I forgot my login password? Can I get a new one?\r\nYes! There are three ways you can update your password:\r\n∙ Click the “Forgot Password” link on the log-in screen\r\n∙ Visit your Settings and click “Change Password”\r\n∙ Request a new password by emailing us</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Payment\r\nWhat payment methods do you accept?\r\nWe accept Visa, MasterCard, and American Express for all Room Design project purchases and for purchasing items from your final design.</p>', 'FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '149-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-16 18:59:15', '2017-04-16 16:59:15', '', 149, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/149-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
