n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">User Content Disclaimer. We are under no obligation to edit or control User Content that you and other users post or publish. We do not endorse, represent, or guarantee the completeness, accuracy, reliability or usefulness of any User Content. We expressly disclaim any and all liability in connection with User Content. However, Space-Filling may at any time and without prior notice, remove any User Content that in our sole judgment violates these Terms and Space-Filling’s Posting Guidelines. You understand that when using the Service you will be exposed to User Content from a variety of sources and acknowledge that User Content may be inaccurate, offensive, indecent or objectionable. You agree to waive, and hereby do waive, any legal or equitable rights or remedies you have or may have against Space-Filling with respect to User Content. You further acknowledge that Space-Filling may review, monitor, edit, control, distribute, refuse to distribute, block access, re-format, alter, distort, delete or remove User Content in order to satisfy any applicable law, enforce our Terms, including Space-Filling’s Posting Guidelines, or protect the rights, property or safety of Space-Filling, Space-Filling users or any third party in our sole discretion. For additional details on our use of User Content, please review our Privacy Policy. Questions regarding User Content and the removal of User Content should be directed to contact@space-filling.com.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><b>Intellectual Property Rights</b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our names, graphics, videos, logos, page headers, button icons, scripts, and service names are our trademarks or trade dress in the European Union and/or other countries (collectively, the "Proprietary Marks"), are owned by Space-Filling. You may not use the Proprietary Marks without our prior writt