(402, 1, '2017-04-20 15:41:34', '2017-04-20 13:41:34', 'Why is elegance in style now considered boring and dull? Maybe it’s for the reason that most people don’t take it accurately enough, because they don’t have a well-developed sense of harmony.\r\n\r\nElegance is a part of our client’s character. Madlen is a lawyer, and as it’s well-known from different magazines, a woman who works as a lawyer is the most attractive Hollywood character, as she is smart, intelligent, modest and a true warrior. She is the incarnation of self-dignity, self-confidence, and yet, softness. The style of her apartment has to combine all these characteristics just like its owner.\r\n\r\nOur task was to create special coziness, combining modern style and classic elements of the interior. Lighting, colors, materials, furniture and décor have to match the owner’s character, help her relax, doing favorite things, like reading or having friends over.\r\n\r\nThe interior included the necessary minimum, contrasts and calmness, womanly rigidity, and a bit of luxury. Chocolate and milk color scheme is the rigidity and calmness. In this interior such straight and fine lines as stability and reliability match harmonically and supplement each other. Dark wood and light textile, elements of brown marble, simple geometry and details make the interior soft and festive. Kitchen space is laconic and modest, functional and roomy; it will be easy to cook in such a kitchen, without feeling uncomfortable because of the lack of space or light. We remembered Madlen’s wish and created large stands for her valuable library in the living room. Kitchen, living room, bedroom and closet are divided with a thin see-through partition, which makes one space flow into another one, and moreover, they can be easily split up when needed. The hero of this story just like many other women dreamt about a spacious closet room with a big wardrobe, lots of hooks and shelves. How could we not make her dream come true?! Silver elements like vases, statues, and lamps make the interior look exquisite, and abstract monochrome paintings add bits of luxury to it.\r\n\r\nThis is how we see elegant home coziness. Why not? Don’t settle for existing stereotypes, as the results of the experiment can be completely breathtaking!', 'Merode 1', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'merode-1__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-21 09:44:28', '2017-06-21 07:44:28', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?post_type=sf_portfolio&#038;p=402', 0, 'sf_portfolio', '', 0),
