(424, 1, '2017-04-21 09:53:46', '2017-04-21 07:53:46', '<span style="color: #2c2c2c;"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">     Some people can’t live without shopping, some are collecting books, and some are very passionate travelers! France, Norway, Belgium, Italy, Greece, England, Germany…our client has been to more than 20 countries! He definitely cannot be called boring! A pleasant companion and interlocutor, a spiritual man, Jacques loves travelling and experiencing the world! “Trying new recipes, listening to unusual music, seeing amazing nature and unique culture, that’s what travelling means to me!” says Jacques.</span></span></span></span>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="color: #2c2c2c;"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">      But just like other people, he also wants to have his own cozy place which is great to come back to, host friends and relatives for a night. For us it was a new task and a new story!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="color: #2c2c2c;"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">     Our design is laconic, functional and cozy for the apartment of a bachelor who likes to have small barbeque parties at his back porch and grow eco-products. We chose truly men’s materials: concrete and wood that were a great match for monochromic ceiling, floor and walls. Simple geometry was just about right! An accent concrete wall is an amazing background for a shelf where this article’s character can place all the souvenirs from different countries. Due to the glazing, Jacques will feel closer to nature; and for more intimate atmosphere, he can easily pull down curtains or blinds! Discreet geometrical pictures and a mat look great around the couch and create a really comfortable rest zone.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="color: #2c2c2c;"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">     Feeling cozy in a man’s place is real! You just need a bit of fantasy and creativity. And what do you think?!</span></span></span></span></p>', 'Stassart 3', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stassart-3__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-21 09:44:28', '2017-06-21 07:44:28', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?post_type=sf_portfolio&#038;p=424', 0, 'sf_portfolio', '', 0),
