(478, 1, '2017-04-21 11:15:51', '2017-04-21 09:15:51', '<p align="justify"><span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">Oh, how great it is when we have young romantic people, full of energy and life, coming to us! Girls will always stay girls! Recently we have been approached by Paul, a talented stylist and make-up artist. Fashion shows, photo sessions, parties and master classes; her life is always so active! Thousands of things and creative ideas! We had an opportunity to create a stylish girly apartment, cozy, luxury, fashionable. A perfect place for sleepovers and morning tea. Every girl dreams of such a place since early childhood, that’s why it was quite easy for us to understand what the client wanted.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">As amazing Christian Dior said, “Pink is tender. And gray is not boring.” And</span></span></span></span> <span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">that</span></span></span></span><span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;">’</span></span></span><span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">s</span></span></span></span> <span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">exactly</span></span></span></span> <span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">what</span></span></span></span> <span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">we</span></span></span></span> <span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">needed</span></span></span></span><span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;">! </span></span></span><span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">The apartment of our client is not big and is located on the mansard floor. But even despite the small size, we managed to create a cozy place. A kitchen zone doesn’t take much space, but is still enough to cook a quick breakfast. The character of this story rarely cooks at home, and this kitchen space has enough functions and comfort. The dining zone is accentuated with a marble wall, which is a pinch of luxury and chic, combined with the texture of dark and light wood. The interior has much lighting, so it feels flowy and airy. Open cabinets and shelves, small poufs and tables, everything is made to enable the owner change the furniture location and make the interior look completely different. A combination of gold and dusty pink is this year’s trend, and was used in our interior, as wonderful golden hanging lamps totally match pink soft elements of the furniture. A bed is the main element of any bedroom, and ours was not the exception. A light bedroom with big and soft bed, through the windows of which one can see an amazing view of the city. Greenery in unobtrusive wireframe flower pots bring freshness and richness to all the rooms, and using spotlight in the interior helps create a romantic mood.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">We are happy we managed to make young Paul’s dream come true! Dream, believe, hope, and all your wishes will definitely come true!</span></span></span></span></p>', 'Merode 2', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'merode-2__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-21 09:44:28', '2017-06-21 07:44:28', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?post_type=sf_portfolio&#038;p=478', 0, 'sf_portfolio', '', 0),
