(513, 1, '2017-04-21 11:31:21', '2017-04-21 09:31:21', '<p align="justify">“<span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">We are young, we are free!” is the motto of our new clients, a wonderful couple, Noel and Annette. It’s amazing to work with such active, smiley and happy people!</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">Usually a living room and a kitchen of small size is an awful pain in the neck. Challenge accepted! It was a chance for us to try ourselves and create a unique design for our beloved clients.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">A recipe of a happy interior in a small space is simple! We chose a great way of visually widening the space, adding fine geometrical lines and transparent partitions – who can resist those?! Favorite colors of our clients, dusty pink and dark blue, are a great match to dark surfaces of wooden wardrobes and shelves. Combination of abstraction and everlasting classics, perky pictures and marble surfaces reflect the portrait of the owners who are ready to face all the challenges, bold ideas and combinations. And a pinch of lush green flowers allows for the freshness and coziness in the house.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="color: #0d0d0d;"><span style="font-family: Cambria, serif;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="en-US">Don’t be afraid to experiment, dear friends! Even the most unreal or crazy idea can be the new beginning of your life! </span></span></span></span></p>', 'Stassart 2', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stassart-2__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-21 09:44:27', '2017-06-21 07:44:27', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?post_type=sf_portfolio&#038;p=513', 0, 'sf_portfolio', '', 0),
