(601, 1, '2017-05-23 09:51:05', '2017-05-23 07:51:05', '<p>Our usual morning starts with a bathroom, a coffee, breakfast and, of course, an important decision – what to wear today. Clothing is part of our image and of our everyday life. Whether you have lots of clothes or just a sufficient amount, they should have a separate place in your home. The location and the size of the wardrobe depend on the possibilities of your home. It may be a simple standing clothes rail, or a wardrobe, or even a walk-in closet. It can become the realisation of your possibilities or ambitions, it helps organise the clothes and the space, but it is important to think through its configuration.</p>', 'Dressing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '256-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-23 09:51:05', '2017-05-23 07:51:05', '', 256, 'http://space-filling.codetiburon.com/256-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
