(637, 1, '2017-06-20 16:11:12', '2017-06-20 14:11:12', '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The time-proven classics, complemented by elements of the modern styles, will certainly help express the elegancy and the luxury of the owners. The attraction of this style lies in the fact that it is never outmoded. Going through the years and saturating the innovations of the present, the classical spaces give a feeling of timelessness and sophistication.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are two actors in this dialogue of time: the space, on the one hand, and the elements, which fill it, on the other hand. These are the walls, which most often possess the pronounced classical features, while the choice of furniture, lighting and decoration is based on the requirements of the modern life – comfort, utility, and convenience.</span></p>\r\n<a href="http://www.bebitalia.com">www.bebitalia.com</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.bebitalia.com">www.miniforms.com</a>', 'The classics forever', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-classics-forever-2__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-23 13:47:54', '2017-06-23 11:47:54', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?p=637', 0, 'post', '', 0),
