(649, 1, '2017-06-21 09:33:00', '2017-06-21 07:33:00', 'Two-bedroom apartment, a young couple’s place where strangers get hosted\r\nMake-over cost : 695.64€ for the living room and kitchen (40.92m²)\r\nFurniture, lighting, accessories budget : 23 555€.\r\n\r\nSimilar people attract each other… is it by accident or a happy coincidence? For our new heroes, their characters and interests work greatly together! Joel and Avril are a sociable and merry couple, young people with both charisma and unique talent! Fantasies do not hold them back! After all, every day they write amazing fairy-tales with magical worlds and unique characters for children’s books.\r\nThis couple is the soul of any company; their home is a place not just for them but also for people from many countries. Our clients are couch-surfers, so they host strangers from all over the world.\r\n\r\n<p align="justify"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-650" src="https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Tollenaere_2.jpg" alt="" width="1635" height="1402" />\r\n\r\nOur clients’ apartment is located in the historical center of Brussels city. In spite of the noise and crowds of people outside, the design should be cozy and practical. The owners need to feel comfortable and their guests need to feel as if they are home too.\r\n\r\nConcrete - a suitable material for the kitchen and living room wall finishes, contrasting nicely with the wooden floor. Dark and light furniture give the room a special atmosphere of comfort. This composition creates an impressive space. But why create such a wall, if our heroes are already impressive?! We just kept the old concrete wall to accentuate the authenticity of the space and to make it look original. A slate board has become another accent wall, and its multifunctionality is just amazing! Recipes of favorite meals, small drawings or notes can be written on it; and sometimes one can just leave a lovely message or kind words of support to your loved one. We even perfectly combined different types of lighting to accentuate certain functional areas, so one can do his job without interfering with each other. Even though the place is quite small, there’s enough room for sports, creativity and for hosting guests. \r\n\r\nThis interior is the portrait of the owners. We tried to embody our heroes’ preferences and characteristics as much as we could. We are ready for new upcoming experiments! No complications or struggles, only our imagination and your wishes!', 'Tollenaere 2', 'Similar people attract each other… is it by accident or a happy coincidence? For our new heroes, their characters and interests work greatly together! Joel and Avril are a sociable and merry couple, young people with both charisma and unique talent! Fantasies do not hold them back! After all, every day they write amazing fairy-tales with magical worlds and unique characters for children’s books.\r\nThis couple is the soul of any company; their home is a place not just for them but also for people from many countries. Our clients are couch-surfers, so they host strangers from all over the world.', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tollenaere-2__trashed', '', '', '2017-06-21 12:31:41', '2017-06-21 10:31:41', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?post_type=sf_portfolio&#038;p=649', 0, 'sf_portfolio', '', 0),
