(708, 26, '2017-06-23 13:33:26', '2017-06-23 11:33:26', '<p>We all work and spend most of our time at work. This is why it is necessary to give thought to your office space. It should inspire your new ideas and favour the work process, it is a space where you will create and work, rest, and create again!</p>\r\n<p>The personal work space should take into account the type of activity of the person who will work there, his or her stylistic preferences, habits and character specificities. Whether it is an office or a home office, it should be comfortable for you to work and be there all the time. Everything should be practical and within reach, with a minimum of distracting elements.</p>', '“Keep calm and work hard” or how work can give more pleasure!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'keep-calm-and-work-hard-or-how-work-can-give-more-pleasure', '', '', '2017-06-23 13:33:26', '2017-06-23 11:33:26', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?p=708', 0, 'post', '', 0),
