(723, 26, '2017-06-23 13:46:44', '2017-06-23 11:46:44', '<p>Early-bird breakfasts, laid-back dinners, and merry suppers – all of this takes place in the kitchen, one of the most important places in the house, its centre, a place to meet the beloved ones and friends. An open kitchen, full of light and air, becomes the studio of taste, both in the literal and in the figurative sense. Therefore, it is very important to think over the whole picture – the organisation of the space, style, colour palette, materials, - as well as the particularities of your kitchen, such as furniture details, fittings, and decoration.</p>', 'Kitchen as the heart of your home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kitchen-as-the-heart-of-your-home', '', '', '2017-06-23 13:46:44', '2017-06-23 11:46:44', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?p=723', 0, 'post', '', 0),
