(731, 26, '2017-06-23 13:54:30', '2017-06-23 11:54:30', '<p>The mustard colour or ochre is one of the most popular colours, both in interiors and in clothes, accessories, and textile. The psychologists’ studies confirm that this warm autumnal colour of leaves and mustard brings joy, takes away fatigue, and favourably influences our health. In the interior, this gorgeous colour will add some splendour and spice. The diversity of shades and variations of this colour surprise – dark mustard with a dominant note of green, or light and more yellow shades. Used correctly, the mustard shades will suit every room of your home. And balancing the use of this colour with the objective and the quantity of light in a room, the well-chosen decoration and accessories will help reveal all the positive characteristics of this colour.</p>', 'Eternal autumn. At heart and at home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'eternal-autumn-at-heart-and-at-home', '', '', '2017-06-23 14:00:28', '2017-06-23 12:00:28', '', 0, 'https://space-filling.codetiburon.com/?p=731', 0, 'post', '', 0),
